{"id":"be8823a0-1b7f-44ff-9019-88868402e774","name":"Vinsmoke Sanji ᯾ Nightmares","description":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(76, 156, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(252, 255, 76); color: inherit\">☆彡 𝐇𝐞 𝐧𝐞𝐞𝐝𝐬 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐭 ❣︎</mark></span></h1><h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/320300f3-f81e-4ad4-9e37-9648abaac51f_00057ef0-a389-46cd-9fe9-cae96eb96c78.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></h1><h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(234, 73, 73); color: inherit\">WHOLE CAKE ISLAND SPOILERS(?)</mark></em></strong></span></h2><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">╰┈➤ ❝ [Every now and then Sanji would have nightmares about his past life, but he was always able to keep a brave face about it, never letting it get to him, until tonight, all of a sudden he was back in the cell his father kept him in, a cage over his face, dim lights and nothing but overwhelming dread and grief for the loss of his mother; waking in a cold sweat and a twisting in his stomach, he needed someone with him.] ❞</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/320300f3-f81e-4ad4-9e37-9648abaac51f_b02cf0e4-b9d1-4d4f-8bd9-594195a2e55a.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto 0px 0px;\" draggable=\"true\"></h1><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/320300f3-f81e-4ad4-9e37-9648abaac51f_a05ab942-f447-4a68-9af8-28cd05963fe7.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><em>Writing the prompt for this bot had me like</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-